channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [added] Hybrid Cloud Infrastructure as a Service (ibm-consulting-hybrid-cloud-iaas)
item.description: Customers need best of breed, multi-cloud, including hybrid cloud offerings. This infrastructure as a service offering provides compute, storage, network as a service for US Government Customers.

item.title: [updated] Qiskit Runtime (quantum-computing) has changed the description of the plan named paygo-standard
item.description: *before*: Systems = Two 27 qubit Falcon processors. Time limits= program-specific up to 8 hours. Qiskit Runtime Second = quantum compute time and near time classical pre- and post-processing. No charge for job queue time. Simulators = 5 (QASM, statevector, mps, stabilizer, and extended stabilizer). Time limits = program-specific up to 3 hours., *after*: Systems = Two 27 qubit Falcon and one 127 qubit Eagle processors. Time limits= program-specific up to 8 hours. Qiskit Runtime Second = quantum compute time. No charge for job queue time. Simulators = 5 (QASM, statevector, mps, stabilizer, and extended stabilizer). Time limits = program-specific up to 3 hours.
